original_title: Queens of the Stone Age: Live at The Wiltern 2013
overview: Live at The Wiltern is the first concert prior to ...Like Clockwork's official touring cycle, on May 23, 2013. It presents a series of song debutes off Queens of the Stone Age's 6th full-length album, ...Like Clockwork. The show was webcasted worldwide and later was included on the Like Clockwork flash drive.
title: Queens of the Stone Age: Live at The Wiltern 2013
